title: Where can I get notes for organic chemistry for JEE? - Quora

response.answer_text: No. Perfect handwritten notes are not usually available. However you can consult MIT lectures on organic chemistry on youtube for notes.

as far as i know best notes are those which are given by best teachers . if you are teached by any good teachers those notes will be suffice. and for reference use jd .lee for reaction mechanism only . it has wonderful theory to understand . cheers .
